---
title: Apricot-Glazed Beyond Meat® Meatball Sandwiches with Garlic-Butter Buns and Cranberry Salad
description: Flavourful apricot spread adds a twist to our glazed Beyond Meat® meatballs! These meatballs are a dinner party classic, but we've packed them into garlic-butter buns to make for an easy grab-and-go supper!

